{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act35side", "eventName": "太陽甩在身後", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AS-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "家傳金拖鞋", "storyInfo": "宣布比賽結果時，因為得到一等獎的人主動棄權，所以佩佩與阿斯帕齊婭都沒能獲得想要的獎品。從阿斯帕齊婭那裡得到寶石的娜仁圖亞決定藉此吸引佩佩上鉤，但陰差陽錯下，寶石卻來到梅捷緹克緹手中。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g4_ctizengarden", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "x": 30.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope02_intro", "key": "$newhope02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "♪河岸上搖曳著紙莎草，河面倒映著青金石♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "♪流過黃金沙丘的長河啊，因寶石的供奉永不乾涸♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "♪願我得見祂漫步河畔，願我隨祂的腳步走向永恆♪", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g4_ctizengarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伴隨著熱烈的掌聲與激昂的合唱，沿著璀璨的寶石大道，獲獎者們機械地往前走著。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "承載了歷史厚重感的莎草船緩緩下沉。黃金拖鞋，來自米諾斯的十枚銀牌，都變成了水面上的一串氣泡。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遺憾？不，我怎麼可能有遺憾呢？見到哈特謝普蘇特女士才是我這次參賽最重要的收穫！", "name": "拉沙德"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比之下，集會名次又有什麼值得在意的呢？……不過，當然，我認為一張失去冠軍的人和冠軍的合影會很有意義。", "name": "拉沙德"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尊敬的哈特謝普蘇特女士，不知道您是否願意賞臉與我合影？如果您願意展示第一名獲得的雕像，那就再好不過了。", "name": "拉沙德"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，當然……謝謝您……", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.3}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash", "volume": 0.3, "channel": "x"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.3, "rfrom": 1.0, "gfrom": 1.0, "bfrom": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.4, "rfrom": 1.0, "gfrom": 1.0, "bfrom": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$skill_flash", "volume": 0.3, "channel": "y"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我參加了一場荒唐的競賽。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，一場荒唐的競賽。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的本意，是對歷史的求索，對英雄偉業的尊敬，對勝利孜孜不倦的追求，以及，對命運的詰問。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，對命運的……什麼東西。總之，你的十枚銀牌變成了一枚新的銀牌。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但別太難過，這裡可是薩爾貢，所以，這還不算失敗。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“地上的黃沙，地下的黃金。”王酋帕夏一句話，沙子就能變得跟金子一樣珍貴。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才的損失不用放在心上，只要哪天機遇來了，你得到了認可，說不定金杯就會免費送給你。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "免費送？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如說，去和拿到金杯的人聊聊，騙他信任你……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你說得很對！", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拿出的寶物得到了認可。這也代表著，米諾斯的文化得到了認可。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕裁判席給出的評價十分淺薄，這些銀牌得到的分數和名次本身足以證明，專業的薩爾貢歷史學者對米諾斯有基本的尊重。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應該跟拿到金杯的收藏家好好談談。他如果也能理解物品背後那段沉重的歷史，或許會願意以一個我負擔得起的價格轉手。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真的認可了嗎？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，如果這樣也算還上了你的人情，那也是好事。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真心感謝，娜仁圖亞。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如那些在白牆下辯論的智者，你點醒了我。我不會失去那些銀牌所代表的榮譽，而且現在我獲得了更多。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比之下，命運如何捉弄我本人，不值得我在乎。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，如果把那些銀牌扔進水中，能幫助人們見到自己想見的影子，那我十分樂意效勞。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果把手裡的這顆寶石扔進水中，也能請來人們口中神靈的影子，那我——", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——等一下！", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看出來你心情變好了，但是冷靜一點，別扔。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有個想法……或者說，我現在就有一個想見的人。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這顆寶石你不太在乎，能不能……借我用用？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g8_sargondeluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#9$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陷阱已經布置好了。", "name": "阿雅妮"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，我工作做得很仔細。越是內行的人越不可能起疑心。", "name": "阿雅妮"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邀約信也悄悄放在那個女孩的包包裡了。我戴了搬運文物用的手套，肯定不會留下痕跡。", "name": "阿雅吉"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後面的事情我來安排。你們對這次計劃還有什麼疑問嗎？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有。我不明白，我們的誘餌為什麼能釣到帕夏之女？", "name": "阿雅吉"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這顆寶石看起來也沒什麼特別的，就像我和阿雅妮那天從下水道裡撈起來的石頭一樣有很多雜質……", "name": "阿雅吉"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有錢人的愛好嘛，不用深究。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚你們在門口盯著，別眨眼睛，不要讓她派人來提前拿走寶石。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，好……我們這次一定不讓你失望。", "name": "阿雅吉"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，我們絕對不會把任何一個人放進來！", "name": "阿雅妮"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_3"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meownormal"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喵？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "jump", "posto": "250,0", "power": 30.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靈巧地避過房間內設下的重重陷阱，米奧來到桌前。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠亮閃閃的瞳孔中，倒映出桌上璀璨的寶石。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_deluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一封匿名信，一張模糊的寶石照片，信中寫了時間地點並要求你獨自前往。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顯而易見，這是一個圈套，你不應該赴約，佩佩。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然要去，不然要怎麼將寶石拿到手。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是什麼？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你答應了今晚帶我去城中的人造湖泊。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應了嗎？或許是你記錯了，有沒有可能是明晚？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換了個腦子後，我從來不會記錯事。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你說的，那幾顆寶石的位置你就記得不是很清楚。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也可以找阿娜特，她最近為你的事寫了很多公文。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實還有一些關於這位古代將領的觀察筆記和幾段論文草稿。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定她願意帶你去。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……或者我還需要再加幾天班。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這封信是誰寄來的，你真的沒有頭緒嗎？", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個拿了第二名的遊客看起來是個好人啊。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，也有可能我在參加豐獲集會時真的表現得太明顯了，人人都能看出我想要的是那塊寶石。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但只有拿到寶石才能從祖拜爾那裡問出更多資訊，無論是我要尋找的寶藏，還是你撰寫論文所需要的資料。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是這樣，我也不建議你冒險。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，即使現在的我已經走遍了薩爾貢也不行？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我記得光是在上學的時候，你就有兩次差點回不來了，幸好我和緹緹去找你。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$2"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，你們就為了讓我評判誰對歷史文獻的解讀更有可信度，專門僱了一支馱獸冒險隊去沙漠裡找我。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$2"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是緹緹在這裡，我說不定就有支持者了。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好她不在。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#8$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……對啊？這麼說來，緹緹去哪裡了？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g2_menatmainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“惹麻煩”……說得就像我想壞她的事一樣。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，文書我也幫她看過一遍了，她應該不會壓力太大在辦公室裡昏倒吧……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_grass", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！什、什麼聲音？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你是我可愛的寶石構裝體，就乖乖地走出來，不要嚇我……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梅捷緹克緹", "content": "……我數到三，你再不出來，我就要用源石技藝了喔。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梅捷緹克緹", "content": "一、二……三！"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "afrom": 0.15, "rfrom": 255.0, "gfrom": 255.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "jump", "posto": "-50,0", "power": 20.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowlong", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喵——！！！！", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，糟了……！怎麼又是這隻小雲獸！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，小傢伙，原諒我……哎呀，摸摸毛，摸摸毛，不要生氣……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你脾氣不好愛抓人，但你聽我解釋，我今天這麼神經質是有原因的！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowshort", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喵嗚……", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得嗎？之前我們一起待在博物館的時候，我就被各種莫名其妙動起來的東西嚇壞了……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……然後，今天我又和阿娜特吵起來了。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拜託了，可愛的小雲獸，你千萬不要像那傢伙一樣對我生氣喔。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_catgrunting", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（發出呼嚕聲）", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，我們總是起爭執，當然，是為學術上的問題爭執。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道她真的很想向公眾展示自己的研究成果。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也知道這次舉辦特展的機會來之不易，所以她非常謹慎，還有點緊張過頭……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許緊張到最後，連自己的初衷都不敢堅持了。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明明是想讓她不要放棄特展啊。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_catgrunting"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅捷緹克緹無意識加快了撫摸的速度。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而米奧因此發出了更加響亮的呼嚕聲。"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但女孩渾然不覺，只是陷入自己的思緒，撫摸小雲獸的動作也越來越快。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前……她說話時聲音小小的，一旦緊張，身體動作就會變得很大。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次她在公眾面前講話，最後大家都會在下面偷笑。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，就算聲音都被笑聲蓋住了，她還是會站在那裡，堅持講完。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唉，真希望她堅持其他事情的勇氣也能來得這麼簡單，只要這樣揉揉她的耳朵就行。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅捷緹克緹雙手包住小雲獸的臉用力揉搓，發洩著自己的情緒，絲毫沒有興趣分辨小雲獸的呼嚕聲是什麼意思。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然，她感覺手心一熱。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚哇，你在吐毛球？！別吐到我的袖子上！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——呃。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一顆寶石？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_deluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者，我一個人去對方指定的地點，在衣服裡藏好監聽器，再找私人警衛埋伏在附近。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間太緊急了，佩佩。現在可是漫灌節前夕，保全公司很難抽調出空閒的人力，我們也不能半夜三更跟人談判。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……你們租一架飛行器隨時準備接應我？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$2"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些能飛的東西會讓人起疑。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$2"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走到門口，揮起一錘直接把大門砸開，把對方嚇住？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$2"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這倒是有可能……", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#4$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但是那樣算不算損壞歷史建築？", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，確實有那麼一點嫌疑，雖然和你的年代比起來不算歷史……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我很喜歡，在我之後的人們生活的痕跡——", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#5$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#10$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚上好啊——諸位——！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#10$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔？佩佩也在？太巧啦。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們猜我剛剛在路上遇到什麼事？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緹緹，你來得正好！我們在商量很重要的事，我需要你的支持……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，快幫我勸勸佩佩。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是發掘重要歷史遺跡的機會，換了你們，難道會為了自己的人身安全就放棄嗎？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$2"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該比我們都清楚，發掘工作最需要的是耐心！現在你只是想追上你弟弟，這簡直是……", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#7$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$2"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，阿娜特，為什麼這次見面，你變得這麼嚴厲……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$2"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，沒人想猜猜看我遇到什麼事了嗎？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你的衣服上沾了很多毛。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝捧場，祖拜爾先生。你猜對啦，我遇到了一隻小雲獸。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我的時代，人們相信雲獸會帶來好運。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我也相信。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——它給我吐了一塊幸運的寶石喔。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#5$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_emoji_proud", "layer": 1.0, "x": 40.0, "y": 170.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼？！", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拜託，讓我看看！", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從阿娜特那裡聽說，她把博物館收藏的那一顆寶石借給了你，所以你同意了投資新展館。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我懂我懂，我會以你的名義追加投資。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$2"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，佩佩。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#3$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望你……不，希望你們答應我一件別的事。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩，阿娜特，還有……祖拜爾先生。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得這顆寶石能讓我們都如願。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}